# This directory is the import target for cognition-university MDX content.
#
# Expected structure after import:
#   content/courses/{slug}/
#     course.en.mdx                              — exports metadata: title, description, duration, difficulty, tag, order, coverImage
#     sections/{section-slug}/section.mdx
#     sections/{section-slug}/lessons/{lesson-slug}.en.mdx
#
# lib/courses.ts currently reads from lib/mock-data.ts. Once content is imported,
# swap its implementation to scan this directory (same function signatures).
